@startmindmap Lakeview High — Smartphone Apps

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam mindmapNode {
    BackgroundColor #EBF8FF
    BorderColor #2B6CB0
    FontSize 11
}

title In-Game Smartphone — App Map

* 📱 Smartphone

** 💬 Contacts & Messaging
*** Text classmates (Rel. gain)
*** Receive story-driven SMS events
*** NPC relationship milestones delivered here
*** Group chats unlock via social events

** 📰 Social Media Feed
*** See posts from classmates
*** React / comment (passive Mood & Rel. modifier)
*** No major story triggers — flavor and hints only
*** Posts reflect NPC arcs (e.g. Camden's anonymous art account)

** 🗓️ Schedule & Calendar
*** View class timetable for the week
*** Upcoming school events and trips
*** Club meeting reminders
*** Player-set reminders (optional QoL feature)

** 🗺️ Navigation Map
*** View town map with all unlocked locations
*** Fast travel via taxi (costs in-game currency)
*** See which locations are available now vs. closed
*** NPC location hints (after certain Rel. stage)

** 🏫 School App
*** Current grades per subject (Knowledge proxy)
*** Attendance record
*** Homework reminders
*** Upcoming exams and mock exam dates

** 🛒 Online Shop
*** Buy consumable items (delivered next day or instantly)
*** Cheaper than some physical shops for common items
*** Some items exclusive to physical shops
*** Unlock new items as story progresses

** ⚙️ Settings
*** Game options (audio, display, controls)
*** Autosave slot viewer
*** Accessibility options

@endmindmap
